name: Cyber Boy
description:
In the city of Ether-net you are "Cyber boy" one of the guardians in charge of maintaining peace against possible techno disasters, in this mission something strange has happened that is causing for layers of cyberspace to flow in and out of existence across the city, collect the Stabiliser Cubes to bring the city back to normal.

Controls
     Move Left      : Left or A
     Move Right   : Right or S
     Jump                 : Space or Up or W
     Grab                  : M or Lshift or Click
